      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOUSIE BOB (6) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but had to settle for a minor placing when a 3.5 lengths third over 400m at this track, clocking 23.09. Rates highly and will give a great sight. DAPHNE ZACAPA (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (23.76) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including six wins. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Must be included in calculations. FASCINATE GEORGE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 400m behind Stop It Zipper (23.54) in a Grade 4/5. Should be in this for a long way. TOMMY TSUNAMI (4) has top-three aspirations after placing last time.",
